    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "They're minting a gold coin with Trump's face. Soon, you can have Trump in your pocket just like Saudi Arabia.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2035193595603689487",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-21T03:15:39+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "\"I think if you don't have clarity about why you're going in, you have no way of knowing how the hell to get out.\" - @GovernorShapiro @RealTimers\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2033982925814043026",
